
params.name: Human-readable name (e.g., "Ondo OUSG")
params.rwaToken: Address of the RWA token contract

cancelScheduledUpgrade().details: Governance can cancel before timelock expires

deposit(uint256).details: Transfers USDC from msg.sender, mints shares, deposits into active RWA

params.usdcAmount: Amount of USDC to deposit (must be >= minDepositAmount)

emergencyWithdrawAll(address).details: Only callable when paused, allows owner to manually rescue funds

executeScheduledUpgrade(uint256).details: Can only be called after UPGRADE_DELAY has passed

params.minAssetsOut: Minimum assets expected after swap (slippage protection)

getBestAPY().details: Queries all active RWAs and returns the best yield

returns.bestRWA: Address of the RWA offering the highest yield

getTotalAssets().details: ERC4626 standard - includes principal + accrued yield

initialize(address,address,string).details: Only callable once by Diamond owner during deployment

params._usdcToken: Address of USDC on this chain

processQueuedWithdrawals().details: Anyone can call this to process pending withdrawals

removeRWAFromWhitelist(address).details: Only callable by Diamond owner. Cannot remove if it's the current active RWA.

params.rwaToken: Address of the RWA to remove

scheduleUpgrade(address).details: Initiates 24-hour timelock before upgrade can execute

params.newRWA: Address of new RWA to upgrade to

setPause(bool).details: Only callable by Diamond owner. Emergency stop mechanism.

params._pause: True to pause, false to unpause

upgradeToRWA(address).details: Only callable by Diamond owner. This is the core innovation:      - Withdraws all assets from old RWA      - Deposits into new RWA      - All users instantly earn new higher yield

params.newRWA: Address of the new RWA to upgrade to (must be whitelisted)

withdraw(uint256).details: Burns shares, withdraws from RWA if needed, returns USDC + earned yield

params.shares: Amount of vault shares to burn

returns.assets: Amount of USDC returned to user

MAX_SLIPPAGE_BPS().notice: Maximum slippage allowed during RWA swap (1% = 100 basis points)

UPGRADE_DELAY().notice: Minimum delay before upgrade can be executed (24 hours)

addRWAToWhitelist(address,string).notice: Add a new RWA to the whitelist

cancelScheduledUpgrade().notice: Cancel a scheduled upgrade - DAO CONTROLLED

deposit(uint256).notice: Deposit USDC into the vault and receive shares

emergencyWithdrawAll(address).notice: Emergency withdrawal (bypass normal flow in critical situations)

executeScheduledUpgrade(uint256).notice: Execute scheduled upgrade (Step 2: After timelock) - DAO CONTROLLED

getBestAPY().notice: Get the highest APY available from whitelisted RWAs

getCurrentAPY().notice: Get the current APY of the active strategy

getCurrentRWA().notice: Get the currently active RWA strategy address

getRWAInfo(address).notice: Get information about a specific RWA

getTotalAssets().notice: Get total value of all assets in the vault

getTotalShares().notice: Get total shares minted across all users

getWhitelistedRWAs().notice: Get list of all whitelisted RWA addresses

initialize(address,address,string).notice: Initialize the vault with USDC address and first RWA

isRWAWhitelisted(address).notice: Check if an RWA is whitelisted

previewDeposit(uint256).notice: Preview how many shares a deposit would receive

previewWithdraw(uint256).notice: Preview how much USDC a withdrawal would receive

processQueuedWithdrawals().notice: Process queued withdrawals (after lock period expires)

removeRWAFromWhitelist(address).notice: Remove an RWA from the whitelist

requestWithdrawal(uint256).notice: Request withdrawal (may be queued if RWA has lock period)

scheduleUpgrade(address).notice: Schedule an upgrade to new RWA (Step 1: Propose) - DAO CONTROLLED

upgradeToRWA(address).notice: Upgrade the vault to a new RWA strategy (THE MAGIC SWITCH)

withdraw(uint256).notice: Withdraw USDC from the vault by burning shares
